Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.75,0:01:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是本田透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.68,0:01:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去年的五月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.55,0:01:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我妈妈因为交通意外过世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.79,0:01:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我开始了秘密的帐篷生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.63,0:01:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在机缘巧合下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.10,0:01:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我开始到同班同学草摩由希同学家寄住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.03,0:01:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 不管是由希、阿夹或紫吴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.37,0:01:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩家的人只要被异性抱到就会变成动物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.65,0:02:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是个不可思议的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.18,0:02:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是件绝对不能告诉任何人的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.36,0:02:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们的活力来源是什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.80,0:02:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我活力的来源是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.10,0:02:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是在期中考结束那段时间才明了自己活力来源是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.45,0:02:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家听好 全部科目里面只要有一科考不及格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.25,0:02:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就得在礼拜天来补考
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.42,0:02:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.35,0:02:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.09,0:02:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们应该要感谢老师特地在假日给你们一个机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.43,0:02:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错 如果不喜欢补考 一开始就别考不及格啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.03,0:02:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透 你一定没问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.21,0:03:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有不及格？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.21,0:03:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,几科？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.61,0:03:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一科啊 那有什么好难过的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.55,0:03:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊 小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.89,0:03:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比起全部不及格的我来说 你实在是幸福多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.46,0:03:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还是难过一点比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.53,0:03:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过小透居然会不及格 我还是第一次看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.73,0:03:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道这次王子没教你吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.67,0:03:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 他有教我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.34,0:03:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.31,0:03:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道你…要补考？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.95,0:03:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,实在是很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.95,0:03:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.45,0:03:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希你还特地教我 我却还考不及格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.69,0:03:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这实在是恩将仇报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.76,0:03:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没有脸见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.43,0:03:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.07,0:03:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.83,0:04:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不要再自责了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.67,0:04:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁都会有状况不好的时候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.37,0:04:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,补考的题目会比较简单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.38,0:04:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一定没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.88,0:04:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊 很轻松的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.82,0:04:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听到你这么说 反而叫我担心起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.99,0:04:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩 时间差不多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.79,0:04:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.36,0:04:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我今天要开学生会 没办法和你一起回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.40,0:04:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你别担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.77,0:04:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真丢脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.31,0:04:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听说你要补考啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.38,0:04:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在干嘛 我不管你罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.32,0:04:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好像越来越沮丧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.33,0:05:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走起路来步履蹒跚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.26,0:05:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真是没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.36,0:05:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像我这么没用 真能顺利的从高中毕业
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.00,0:05:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完成当初和妈妈的约定吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.67,0:05:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我居然会不及格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.78,0:05:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我突然觉得头好晕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.48,0:05:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样子 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.68,0:05:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.65,0:05:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么不能再坚强点…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.26,0:05:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.30,0:05:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在干嘛啦 不需要这么难过的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.37,0:05:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.20,0:05:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这样最后会发烧喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.71,0:05:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.21,0:05:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发烧啊！我才刚说就发烧啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.85,0:05:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.32,0:05:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.88,0:05:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真危险 怎么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.29,0:06:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发烧啊…真的发烧啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.79,0:06:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,38度2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.90,0:06:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透的病名是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.57,0:06:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感冒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.27,0:06:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这我知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.61,0:06:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点去睡觉啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.71,0:06:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系 吃了药就没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.51,0:06:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还得去买晚餐的菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.35,0:06:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别买了 快睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.28,0:06:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对别人的感冒就那么在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.15,0:06:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么自己感冒就毫不在乎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.92,0:06:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我今天还要打工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.86,0:06:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翘一天班算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.06,0:06:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.23,0:06:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.63,0:06:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天什么事都别做 安心休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.14,0:06:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了睡觉不能做其他事喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.74,0:06:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.74,0:06:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.41,0:06:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乖小孩要听话喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.75,0:06:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.05,0:07:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 乖孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.42,0:07:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.76,0:07:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么偏在这种时候发烧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.36,0:07:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是更叫我丢脸吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.77,0:07:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么 小透感冒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.11,0:07:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她没事吧 有在休息吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.04,0:07:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红叶 你太大声了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.38,0:07:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是为了让她好好休息 我才叫她别去打工的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.75,0:07:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以她今天不会去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.05,0:07:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊 知道了 交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.96,0:07:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天小透感冒请假一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.86,0:07:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我今天来替她做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.23,0:07:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连小透的份一起…我会卖力打扫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.77,0:07:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他到底是哪里来的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.11,0:08:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了 反正挺可爱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.74,0:08:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无所谓了 这么可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.82,0:08:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发烧时要怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.28,0:08:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感冒时要怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.69,0:08:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种时候就要吃韭菜…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.59,0:08:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感冒吃韭菜最有效了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.00,0:08:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感冒时吃韭菜最棒了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.56,0:08:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,韭菜是治感冒的万灵丹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.33,0:08:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这也是韭菜 这也是韭菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.70,0:08:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.64,0:08:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 不看了 混帐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.11,0:08:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每一本都只会说韭菜韭菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.88,0:08:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,韭菜根本不是人吃的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.89,0:08:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹 天气放晴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.91,0:09:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我烧到40度左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.22,0:09:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以希望截稿日期能够延到下个礼拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.46,0:09:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么 老师 你这样实在过分了点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.43,0:10:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行了 我头好晕 又好冷 而且想吐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.07,0:10:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快死了～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.74,0:10:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你没事吧 老师…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.97,0:10:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.91,0:10:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老师～！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.45,0:10:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.68,0:10:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？阿夹你在干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.49,0:10:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看了不就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.22,0:10:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,韭菜？难道是为了小透？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.86,0:10:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总不能叫病人自己煮饭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.91,0:10:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干嘛 有疑问吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.41,0:10:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我什么都没说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.58,0:10:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 我们的晚饭呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.71,0:10:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然是叫外卖啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.58,0:10:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有事拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.39,0:11:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.75,0:11:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以帮我端给她吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.02,0:11:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.09,0:11:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 我自己端！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.07,0:11:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弄坏家里的东西要罚钱哦 罚钱 罚钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.11,0:11:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,扭扭捏捏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.89,0:11:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.63,0:11:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.57,0:11:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹你特地帮我做的啊 好棒 我好高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.94,0:11:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别说了 你快吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.67,0:11:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 我要开动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.92,0:12:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好吃喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.69,0:12:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃完的碗盘就放到走廊上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.96,0:12:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.56,0:12:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.93,0:12:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然你会这么想 就不要感冒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.40,0:12:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.07,0:12:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.88,0:12:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别哭喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.74,0:12:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对…对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.65,0:12:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干嘛啦 说吧 有什么心事就说出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.32,0:12:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很想完成和妈妈的约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.53,0:12:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我却考不及格 我真的很没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.60,0:12:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不仅对不起由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.47,0:12:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚至还感冒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.54,0:13:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想要成为更精明的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.78,0:13:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说完了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.58,0:13:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.25,0:13:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是考不及格也可以靠补考来挽回啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.79,0:13:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在意那个笨蛋由希干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.59,0:13:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尽量指使他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.00,0:13:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让他做牛做马都没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.33,0:13:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你真的觉得自己感冒很对不起大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就快点好起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.70,0:13:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再像以前那样成天傻笑地在家里晃来晃去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.64,0:13:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傻笑？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.64,0:13:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然我总觉得…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.99,0:13:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.36,0:13:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,觉得心烦气燥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.43,0:14:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以在你可以晃来晃去之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.70,0:14:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会帮你做饭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.51,0:14:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以 你不要瞎操心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.75,0:14:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.52,0:14:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 快吃 不然烧不会退喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.65,0:14:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.22,0:14:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.72,0:14:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种东西哪里好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.59,0:14:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和你做的菜比起来根本…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.33,0:14:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个也就是说…是在鼓励我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.28,0:14:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.71,0:14:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你变精明了那才叫人难以忍受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.35,0:14:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好高兴喔 阿夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.30,0:15:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你回来啦 怎么这么晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.90,0:15:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.24,0:15:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,实在 实在太放肆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.74,0:15:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和小透辛苦种的韭菜居然被…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.48,0:15:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是谁那么过分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.88,0:15:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是憎恨韭菜的人所做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.39,0:15:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有人说是你 放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.70,0:15:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紫吴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.80,0:15:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告诉你吧 真的要讲起来 凶手就是小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.71,0:15:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.61,0:15:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过小透在回家途中因为发烧而昏倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.88,0:15:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直在楼上躺着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.64,0:15:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猜谜时间到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.95,0:15:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请问 她到底是如何到你的菜园里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.41,0:15:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偷摘你的韭菜呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.68,0:15:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发烧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.69,0:16:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她刚吃完东西睡着 别吵醒她喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.00,0:16:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你煮什么给她吃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.13,0:16:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,韭菜稀饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.64,0:16:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想打架吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.15,0:16:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打架时请保持肃静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.15,0:16:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然会吵醒小透的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.99,0:16:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我来晚了 抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.36,0:16:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欢迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.10,0:16:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我听说姊姊身体不舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.70,0:16:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为看她快哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.41,0:16:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我带她一起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.71,0:16:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她知道你来看她一定会很高兴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.65,0:17:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.69,0:17:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透她没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.59,0:17:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全都来啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.29,0:17:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位 先进来再说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.60,0:17:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底要撑到何时 臭老鼠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.10,0:17:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快把你的拳放下来 笨猫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.81,0:17:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透 你觉得如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.58,0:17:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢 我好多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.85,0:17:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.85,0:17:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.22,0:17:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,病人躺着就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.26,0:17:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的 不能温柔一点吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.20,0:17:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是嘛 小透是小女生耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.97,0:17:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我那时候不一样 你要温柔一点喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.00,0:17:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像捧着易碎品一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.71,0:18:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道他对你动粗过？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.71,0:18:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.95,0:18:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他给我打了好粗的针 简直像给马打的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.62,0:18:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一边说打错了 一边一直用针戳我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.65,0:18:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还问我说痛不痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.89,0:18:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别说了 孩子们会害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.73,0:18:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要打错罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.00,0:18:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果小透喊痛就别打了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.87,0:18:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事的 一点都不痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.77,0:18:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是紫吴说会痛耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.81,0:18:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是故意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.24,0:18:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿波 你好过分哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.08,0:18:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然故意作弄人家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.75,0:18:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁叫你要在那边乱抱怨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.19,0:18:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟 医药费…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.49,0:18:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还是快点好起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.73,0:18:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你一直躺在床上 会有好几个家伙浑身不对劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.87,0:19:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有事就叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.17,0:19:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连波鸟叔叔都不对劲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.44,0:19:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没那种事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.65,0:19:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦！叔叔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.48,0:19:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对哦 杞纱你12岁 波鸟先生他27岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.75,0:19:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差15岁是该叫叔叔啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.42,0:19:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 那你怎么叫紫吴和绫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.83,0:19:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紫吴叔叔 绫女叔叔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.87,0:19:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.04,0:19:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以进来吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.21,0:19:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.58,0:19:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟说你应该差不多好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.58,0:19:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 抱歉让你担心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.35,0:19:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.95,0:19:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先把这个给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.25,0:19:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.02,0:19:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我帮你把补考可能会出的题目都整理出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.19,0:19:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.32,0:20:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要做熟了这些题目 我想补考一定没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.49,0:20:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等你好了之后再一起温习吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.41,0:20:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.62,0:20:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是为了自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.56,0:20:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道除了韭菜没其他的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.73,0:20:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干嘛 在准备新娘课程啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.50,0:20:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才不是 笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.30,0:20:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.30,0:20:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了 是为了小透吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.37,0:20:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了 小鬼到一边去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.74,0:20:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！阿夹打人家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.28,0:20:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了 真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.98,0:20:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是为了自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.38,0:21:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是希望能让别人快点复原的这种心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.59,0:21:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟 你想吃小透亲手做的哪些料理？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.63,0:21:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
